sources.description:
Franck Denard (Alan Delabie) sets out on the trail of the mysterious Wagner (Patrick Kilpatrick) who had made him a human guinea pig without his knowledge. But he must first settle scores with Pietro (Afif Benbadra), who has become number one in the Malandrain criminal organization in Europe. Franck will have to face his demons in an attempt to save the people he loves.

2022. Stars: Eric Roberts, Louis Mandylor, Costas Mandylor
